Instructions
    Use the pyinotify for monit to directory that if directory have some changes.
    Changes detected after,the daemon will read it ,then establish a connection with the scribe log server,sending log to scribe.

How to?
    client.py is main program.It run as a daemon.
    Befor use,edit client.py,modify the keyword:"host","port" for services corresponding to your scribe listen.
    python client start|stop|restart
